04)------MatchRecognizePattern: order_by=[stock_price.price_date ASC NULLS LAST] pattern=[A]
05)--------Projection: stock_price.company, stock_price.price_date, stock_price.price, upper(stock_price.company) = Utf8("ACME") AS __mr_symbol_A
